name: Jasmine Laverne
summary: Jasmine Laverne, a 34-year-old Film Director based in Los Angeles, is seeking a long-term, monogamous relationship. Fluent in English and Spanish, she holds a degree from the University of Michigan and works in the Entertainment industry. Hailing from Atlanta, Georgia, she takes pride in her creativity, independence, and kindness. Her interests include film, yoga, reading, and vegan cooking. She identifies as a Gay woman and primarily uses she/her/hers pronouns. She is of Black African descent, does not smoke or do drugs, and only drinks on occasion. Being an active individual, she likes to exercise regularly. She owns a cat and a dog and hopes to have children one day. As a Virgo and an INFJ, Jasmine tends to be introspective, spiritual, and liberal. When it comes to potential partners, Jasmine prefers women between 30 and 40 years old who do not smoke or do drugs but enjoy a drink now and then and maintain an active lifestyle. She hopes to meet a partner who also wants children.
